import "./App.css";
import NavBar from "./components/NavBar";
import { BrowserRouter as Router,  Route, Routes } from "react-router-dom";
import { Home } from "./components/Pages/Home";
import { Inventory } from "./components/Pages/Inventory";
import { Blog } from "./components/Pages/Blog";
import { Contact } from "./components/Pages/Contact";
import {useMatch} from 'react-router-dom'
import obucaService from './services/obuca'
//If I am to avoid redux and all that jazz, 
//I am to decalre here bunch of state hooks and pass them to inventory for view and navbar for fetch setting shit
//still seems easier then redux
function App() {
  /*const match = useMatch('/inventory/:id')  
  const obuca = match ?  obucaService
  .get(match.params.id).then(response) : null*/
  return (
    <>
      <Router>
        <NavBar />
      
        
          <Routes>
            <Route path="/" element={<Home />} />
            <Route path="/inventory" >
              <Route path="women"> 
              <Route path="patike" element={<Inventory path={'/women/patike'}/>}/>
                <Route path="cipele"  element={<Inventory path={'/women/cipele'}/>}></Route>
                <Route path="papuce"></Route>
                <Route path="sandale"></Route>
                <Route path="cizme"></Route>
                <Route path="stikle"></Route>
              </Route>
              <Route path="man"> 
                <Route path="patike"></Route>
                <Route path="cipele"></Route>
                <Route path="papuce"></Route>
                <Route path="sandale"></Route>
                <Route path="cizme"></Route>
              </Route>
              <Route path="child"> 
              <Route path="patike"></Route>
                <Route path="cipele"></Route>
                <Route path="papuce"></Route>
                <Route path="sandale"></Route>
                <Route path="cizme"></Route>
              </Route>
              <Route path="sale"> 
              <Route path="patike"></Route>
                <Route path="cipele"></Route>
                <Route path="papuce"></Route>
                <Route path="sandale"></Route>
                <Route path="cizme"></Route>
              </Route>
            </Route>
            <Route path="/blog" element={<Blog />} />
            <Route path="/contact" element={<Contact />} />
          </Routes>
        
      </Router>
  </>
  );
}

export default App;
